\begin{document}$ f_{CGN} = \pi _{C} / (\pi _{C} + \pi _{A} (\pi _{A} + \pi _{G})) $\end{document}, and the probability of disappearance of the CGN block is \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
